ABOUT US

" At LJC Farmyard, we pride ourselves on offering 100% organic and non-GMO fruits, vegetables, and related products. Leveraging traditional breeding techniques in our state-of-the-art facilities, we meticulously verify the authenticity of our seeds, sourced from Russia, to ensure their organic integrity and wholesomeness for consumption. We cater to a diverse range of clients through our wholesale and retail services, facilitating seamless B2B, B2C, and C2C transactions. "

" Our state-of-the-art warehouse operates with a robust workforce of 3,000 employees, divided into two dedicated departments: 1,500 personnel focus on fruits and related products, while another 1,500 specialize in vegetables and their derivatives. As part of the expansive LJC Farmyard network, which boasts a 30,000-strong workforce, we are committed to delivering exceptional 'Quality-Equity-Organic' experiences to our valued clients, both domestically in Ghana and internationally. "
